rea": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-450b8b9c6aac4a42b856363c79f95067_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "82 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/609195242"}}, "attached_info": "ClUIxsLdx7v2xZMPEAMaCDk3NjU3NDU0INDh76QGMAA4+gpACnIJNjA5MTk1MjQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1688029484.654956", "card_id": "Q_264341373", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何解决 async/await 的传染性？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "async/await 是 Generator 函数的语法糖，是对 Promise 的封装。 但它是具有传染性的： 如果一个底层函数使用了 async，那么所有基于它的所有调用链都必须使用 await 获取结果，或者使用 .then()。 依然没有解决 「 用同步方式写异步程序 」 的问题啊。 但 node 内置库中有一些使异步操作阻塞变成同步函数的方法，例如： fs.readFile(path[, options], callback) fs.readFileSync(path[, options]) 如何写一个包含异步操作的普通函数，使其阻塞，而不用使用 .then() 来获取结果？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-0f398092b3562f4e857a0ef3875e186e_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "80 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/264341373"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IxsLdx7v2xZMPEAMaCDIwMTY3MzQ0IOOg59EFMAA4gwFAC3IJMjY0MzQxMzczeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1688029484.655949", "card_id": "Q_37064172", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "东吴后期到底是个什么局面，为何在蜀被灭后还支撑了十数年？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "拜演义所赐，三国中吴国的存在感一直不强，但这个国家反而是三国中最后一个灭亡的，甚至是晋朝建立后十多年才被灭掉。这个国家，对外不乏大战役，除了赤壁夷陵，包括石亭之战亦